							<div class="elementor-shortcode">        <button
            class="kkbs-bw-toggle-btn"
            type="button"
            aria-pressed="false"
            data-bw-toggle
        >
            <span class="kkbs-bw-toggle-label-on">Ó╣éÓĖ½ÓĖĪÓĖöÓĖéÓĖ▓ÓĖ¦ÓĖöÓĖ│ <br/>(Grayscale Mode)</span>
            <span class="kkbs-bw-toggle-label-off">Ó╣éÓĖ½ÓĖĪÓĖöÓĖøÓĖüÓĖĢÓĖ┤ <br/>(Normal Mode)</span>
